trustget (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  - Smart download with progress bar and resume support
  - Automatic checksum verification (SHA256/SHA512/MD5)
  - GitHub Releases integration with metadata extraction
  - Trust score engine with transparent scoring (0-100)
  - GPG signature verification
  - Sandbox execution support
  - JSON output for CI/CD integration

